-- Cuban Puig Signs $42 Million Contract With Dodgers, ESPN Says
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-06-28T16:38:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/cuban-puig-signs-42-million-contract-with-dodgers-espn-says.html
The Los Angeles Dodgers will sign
Cuban outfielder Yasel Puig to a seven-year contract worth $42
million, ESPN reported on its website, citing people familiar
with the situation.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
